title: Policy5132a(s1)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Eligibility for competing on interscholastic teams and participating in intramural and co-curricular clubs is determined by a student's academic standing.

If a student does not have a C- average or better, he/she can practice but not play.

Eligibility is determined bi-weekly. Decisions will hold for the subsequent two-week period.
